This script get the info of the businesses. The script compatible with python27 and any OS.

- Dependency
    scrapy
- How to run?
  In cmd windows, go to the project folder and run following command;
        python main.py --city [city name] --start [start date] --end [end date] --increment [increment]
        ex: python main.py --city Tokyo --start 21/08/2018 --end 31/08/2018 --increment 2 --currency USD
            python main.py --hotel_name the-fullterton-singapore --start 21/08/2018 --end 31/08/2018 --increment 2 --currency USD

       -*- increment option is 1 as a default.